<p>
<note n="0535002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0535002">Daśabhūmīśvara.</note>
<note n="0535003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0535003">1. Pramuditā-bodhisattvabhūmi.</note>
<note n="0535004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0535004">Parinirmita-devabhavana.</note>
<note n="0535005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0535005">菩薩原語後出</note>
<note n="0535006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0535006">金剛藏. Vajragarbha.</note>
<note n="0535007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0535007">大乘光明. Mahāyānaprabhāva.</note>
<note n="0535008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0535008">Vairocana.</note>
<note n="0535009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0535009">Mahāpratisaṃvibhūmi.</note>
